data.description: Quant 3 bedroom, 2 bath home built with energy efficiency in mind. 2x6 outer wall construction, dual pane thermal windows, central heat, free standing propane stove with native rock backing. New laminate and carpeting throughout - and a fresh coat of paint. Several windows with great natural light. Slider leads to large wood deck with covered spa. Nice kitchen cabinets with new hardware, newer appliances including double oven and propane range. Granite counters in kitchen and master bath. Walk in tub/shower in hallway bath. Whole house propane generator for those occasions when PGE goes down - recently serviced. Paved driveways on both sides of the home. Usable 2.5 acres with several mature Oaks and pines. RV/Trailer pad with hookups. Two outbuildings and one attached - great for workshop and storage.
